  title: Selling Cheap
  description: High Pontiff, one of our clerics was procuring supplies for his parish
    when he chanced upon a strange foreign merchant. The man claimed to be weary
    of the city and longed for his homeland, and thus he was liquidating all his
    wares at a pittance. This could truly be the bargain of the century!
